{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Good morning."},{"time":2000,"text":"Let's look for a minute at the greatest icon of all, Leonardo da Vinci."},{"time":7000,"text":"We're all familiar with his fantastic work --"},{"time":10000,"text":"his drawings, his paintings, his inventions, his writings."},{"time":13000,"text":"But we do not know his face."},{"time":15000,"text":"Thousands of books have been written about him,"},{"time":18000,"text":"but there's controversy, and it remains, about his looks."},{"time":22000,"text":"Even this well-known portrait is not accepted by many art historians."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"So, what do you think?"},{"time":29000,"text":"Is this the face of Leonardo da Vinci or isn't it?"},{"time":32000,"text":"Let's find out."},{"time":35000,"text":"Leonardo was a man that drew everything around him."},{"time":38000,"text":"He drew people, anatomy, plants, animals, landscapes, buildings, water, everything."},{"time":46000,"text":"But no faces?"},{"time":48000,"text":"I find that hard to believe."},{"time":50000,"text":"His contemporaries made faces, like the ones you see here --"},{"time":53000,"text":"en face or three-quarters."},{"time":55000,"text":"So, surely a passionate drawer like Leonardo"},{"time":58000,"text":"must have made self-portraits from time to time."},{"time":62000,"text":"So let's try to find them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"I think that if we were to scan all of his work"},{"time":67000,"text":"and look for self-portraits, we would find his face looking at us."},{"time":71000,"text":"So I looked at all of his drawings, more than 700,"},{"time":75000,"text":"and looked for male portraits."},{"time":78000,"text":"There are about 120, you see them here."},{"time":81000,"text":"Which ones of these could be self-portraits?"},{"time":83000,"text":"Well, for that they have to be done as we just saw, en face or three-quarters."},{"time":88000,"text":"So we can eliminate all the profiles."},{"time":91000,"text":"It also has to be sufficiently detailed."},{"time":93000,"text":"So we can also eliminate the ones that are very vague or very stylized."},{"time":99000,"text":"And we know from his contemporaries"},{"time":101000,"text":"that Leonardo was a very handsome, even beautiful man."},{"time":104000,"text":"So we can also eliminate the ugly ones or the caricatures."},{"time":108000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"And look what happens -- only three candidates remain that fit the bill."},{"time":114000,"text":"And here they are."},{"time":116000,"text":"Yes, indeed, the old man is there,"},{"time":118000,"text":"as is this famous pen drawing of the Homo Vitruvianus."},{"time":121000,"text":"And lastly, the only portrait of a male that Leonardo painted, \"The Musician.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"Before we go into these faces,"},{"time":128000,"text":"I should explain why I have some right to talk about them."},{"time":131000,"text":"I've made more than 1,100 portraits myself"},{"time":135000,"text":"for newspapers, over the course of 300 -- 30 years, sorry, 30 years only."},{"time":139000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":140000,"text":"But there are 1,100, and very few artists have drawn so many faces."},{"time":145000,"text":"So I know a little about drawing and analyzing faces."},{"time":148000,"text":"OK, now let's look at these three portraits."},{"time":151000,"text":"And hold onto your seats, because if we zoom in on those faces,"},{"time":154000,"text":"remark how they have the same broad forehead, the horizontal eyebrows,"},{"time":158000,"text":"the long nose, the curved lips and the small, well-developed chin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"I couldn't believe my eyes when I first saw that."},{"time":164000,"text":"There is no reason why these portraits should look alike."},{"time":166000,"text":"All we did was look for portraits that had the characteristics of a self-portrait,"},{"time":170000,"text":"and look, they are very similar."},{"time":172000,"text":"Now, are they made in the right order?"},{"time":175000,"text":"The young man should be made first."},{"time":177000,"text":"And as you see here from the years that they were created,"},{"time":179000,"text":"it is indeed the case."},{"time":181000,"text":"They are made in the right order."},{"time":183000,"text":"What was the age of Leonardo at the time? Does that fit?"},{"time":185000,"text":"Yes, it does. He was 33, 38 and 63 when these were made."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188000,"text":"So we have three pictures, potentially of the same person"},{"time":192000,"text":"of the same age as Leonardo at the time."},{"time":194000,"text":"But how do we know it's him, and not someone else?"},{"time":197000,"text":"Well, we need a reference."},{"time":199000,"text":"And here's the only picture of Leonardo that's widely accepted."},{"time":203000,"text":"It's a statue made by Verrocchio, of David,"},{"time":206000,"text":"for which Leonardo posed as a boy of 15."},{"time":208000,"text":"And if we now compare the face of the statue,"},{"time":211000,"text":"with the face of the musician, you see the very same features again."},{"time":215000,"text":"The statue is the reference, and it connects the identity of Leonardo"},{"time":218000,"text":"to those three faces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, this story has not yet been published."},{"time":225000,"text":"It's only proper that you here at TED hear and see it first."},{"time":228000,"text":"The icon of icons finally has a face."},{"time":231000,"text":"Here he is: Leonardo da Vinci."},{"time":233000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}